{"type": "article", "id": 24530, "title": "波纹玻璃纤维板桌子", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-28T06:04:37Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 23, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607104132mpKacWkV0R6obCrA.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">上周我们介绍过美国设计师 Louie Rigano “印出树影的窗帘”，这是他最新设计的桌子。他使用了有波纹的玻璃纤维板作为桌面、支柱和隔板，不同面之间都像积木一样相互拼接，玻璃的转折之间形成了微妙的光影变化，很轻盈。桌面上另有一块与波纹桌面相嵌的移动木板，可以放杯子等茶具。<a href=\"http://www.louierigano.com/Interface-Table\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104129w5OsWKDArfFcQ26b.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.59791667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104130saMUXkKr6OAI5jNn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.4875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104130r4mAbsUnCLV8GTaX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104131ifM0B9gtjlqvrWz4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104131YWesEQ7xN69A41zq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}